This project includes original work by Kishor Chandrakant Naik, an independent consultant and senior software architect. It is designed to empower engineering teams through scalable backend architecture, modular onboarding flows, and production-grade developer experience.

Significant contributions include:
- Express.js + TSOA + TypeScript boilerplate architecture
- PM2 clustering and benchmarking setup
- Developer-friendly documentation with expressive formatting and icon usage
- Dockerized local development and onboarding guides

